{"tid":2290354,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"小三小朋友學英文, 求提議","createTime":"2020-11-18T03:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T08:24:29.000Z","uid":206687,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb9d2858041fe865619be8f43f60dd74eb28638","tid":2290354,"uid":206687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:02:13.000Z","msg":"小朋友今年小三<br />\n自覺學校教得OK <br />\n自己英文比較一般<br />\n當然唔打算再去打亂佢學習<br />\n同都抱住要信任老師嘅想法<br />\n小朋友本身都鐘意聽故仔<br />\n有冇咩短篇英文故仔網可以推薦<br />\n適合返佢程度<br />\n想話等佢試睇一次<br />\n如果小朋友覺得唔適合<br />\n就都唔會勉強<br />\n如果適合咪寓學習於娛樂<br />\n或者有冇其他建議<br />\n我唔想自己英文差仲迫住同小朋友講<br />\n同佢講好廣東話就算<br />\n我本身都好難提供一個英文學習環境<br />\n放學做功課就算<br />\n同我都抗拒要補習"},{"pid":"3d2a1dccad46dc0f6f444895fd6fcbcb7564e18d","tid":2290354,"uid":301258,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:09:52.000Z","msg":"睇youtube 好過啦<br />\nyoutube 大把英文教材"},{"pid":"cd217dca30953e2b6bab0723bea7e5e202a12511","tid":2290354,"uid":360183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:11:51.000Z","msg":"去啲洋人多既興趣班 足球欖球<br />\n唔洗迫佢學 身邊啲朋友講自然會識講"},{"pid":"3499f627ab8184a3df292d4a99b53947be1c539c","tid":2290354,"uid":206687,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d2a1dccad46dc0f6f444895fd6fcbcb7564e18d","tid":2290354,"uid":301258,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:09:52.000Z","msg":"睇youtube 好過啦<br />\nyoutube 大把英文教材"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:20:02.000Z","msg":"我望下先 thanks<br />\n有冇咩channel你特別推薦"},{"pid":"24ed3ff6a13a822044f25515c81a7831345c234c","tid":2290354,"uid":360183,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"3499f627ab8184a3df292d4a99b53947be1c539c","tid":2290354,"uid":206687,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d2a1dccad46dc0f6f444895fd6fcbcb7564e18d","tid":2290354,"uid":301258,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:09:52.000Z","msg":"睇youtube 好過啦<br />\nyoutube 大把英文教材"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T03:20:02.000Z","ms